<Layout title="Construction CRM: How to Build a Sales Pipeline That Wins More Bids | BuildWorkPro" description="Construction CRM tips for subcontractors. Build a sales pipeline, track leads, improve follow-ups, and increase your bid win rate.">
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-32 pb-20">
    <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
